if_true_right_eq_or:

@[simp]
theorem if_true_right_eq_or (p : Prop) [h : decidable p] (q : Prop) : (if p then q else true) = (¬p ∨ q) := by
  by_cases p <;> simp [h]
#align if_true_right_eq_or if_true_right_eq_or
if_true_left_eq_or:
@[simp]
theorem if_true_left_eq_or (p : Prop) [h : decidable p] (q : Prop) : (if p then true else q) = (p ∨ q) := by
  by_cases p <;> simp [h]
#align if_true_left_eq_or if_true_left_eq_or
if_false_right_eq_and:
@[simp]
theorem if_false_right_eq_and (p : Prop) [h : decidable p] (q : Prop) : (if p then q else false) = (p ∧ q) := by
  by_cases p <;> simp [h]
#align if_false_right_eq_and if_false_right_eq_and
if_false_left_eq_and:
@[simp]
theorem if_false_left_eq_and (p : Prop) [h : decidable p] (q : Prop) : (if p then false else q) = (¬p ∧ q) := by
  by_cases p <;> simp [h]
#align if_false_left_eq_and if_false_left_eq_and
